,"side":"bottom"}},{"element":"app-data-table thead th:nth-child(7)","popover":{"title":"Ordered vs. Received","description":"The Ordered column shows total units across all lines. The Received column shows how many have arrived. When Received equals Ordered, the PO status automatically moves to Received.","side":"bottom"}}]}"""
